 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003ELoyalli is a mobile application, available on iPhone and Android that keeps loyalty cards on your phone.  Loyalli provides retailers with a free stamp card loyalty service such as the classic: \u201cBuy 9 get one free\u201d without the printing costs.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ECustomers no longer have to carry numerous cards around with them in order to accrue enough stamps to redeem the offers from retailers.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003ERetailers can choose their offer and amend it at any time. Loyalli then provides statistics to the retailer on how successful their loyalty scheme is.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe app will identify which retailers nearby have a stamp card offer through Loyalli.\u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EIncludes full social media integration.\u003C/p\u003E",
